  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eLike the best examples of contemporary design, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.n4architecture.co.uk/projects/birch-pavilion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBirch Pavilion\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e in London’s Stoke Newington reveals its sophistication through restraint, allowing the existing landscape to guide its form and function. As the name suggests, light filters through three birch trees, casting dappled shadows across a micro cement floor – an interplay of nature and built form that captures the essence of \u003ca href=\"https://www.n4architecture.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eN4 Architecture’s\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e design philosophy. The backyard pavilion features sustainable materials and acoustic design for a multipurpose workspace and music room.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570154\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570154\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-13-810x1134.jpg\" alt=\"A modern wooden interior office with a desk, chair, dual monitors, and bookshelves. Large door open to a fenced yard with birch trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1134\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-13-810x1134.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-13-800x1120.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-13-768x1075.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-13-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-13-810x1134.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570155\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570155\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-2-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden home office with large window, chair, desk with dual monitors, bookshelves filled with books, and a potted plant.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-2-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-2-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInside, a carefully considered material palette negotiates between competing demands. Here, acoustical requirements for music listening are met through cork ceiling panels, while birch plywood joinery creates visual continuity with the trees beyond. A table placed strategically within this space serves both as a workstation and as a point of contemplation, oriented to frame views of the garden through the building’s permeable structure.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570152\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570152\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-12-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden shelves filled with neatly arranged CDs and vinyl records in a room with a wooden interior.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-12-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-12-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-12-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eN4 goes on to say: “Our clients came to us with a clear vision: they wanted a low-maintenance building that would stand the test of time, blending effortlessly into the landscape. Their decision to stay in this home for the long term drove everything about this project. The brief was clear: working space area and shelving for the beautiful CD collection to listen to music. We chose durable, sustainable materials to reflect that vision. For us, sustainability begins with thoughtful material choices, ensuring this space ages gracefully while minimizing its environmental impact. The primary structure is made of timber, a low carbon, renewable resource, and the metal cladding is fully reusable. Inside, birch plywood joinery continues the natural theme, while cork ceilings enhance acoustics for music listening.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570151\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570151\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-6-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Room with a gray sofa and a wall-mounted bookshelf filled with books and CDs, next to a window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-6-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-6-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-6-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-6-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-6-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570150\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570150\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-10-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Open wooden window with views of greenery, next to a wall-mounted shelf filled with CDs and a pendant light bulb hanging from the ceiling. A portion of a gray sofa is visible.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-10-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-10-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-10-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-10-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-10-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570153\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570153\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-5-810x1134.jpg\" alt=\"Interior with wooden ceiling beams, a small shelf holding green plants, and part of a desk with computer monitors. Brick wall visible through a narrow window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1134\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-5-810x1134.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-5-800x1120.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-5-768x1075.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-5-1097x1536.jpg 1097w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-5-810x1134.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe pavilion’s relationship with its site merits particular attention. Rather than dominating the garden’s peripheral, it acts as a mediator between manicured and wild space. From the outside, the pavilion’s subtle circular design reveals itself gradually. The repetition of vertical timber beams – each precisely placed yet appearing organic in their spacing – creates a permeable boundary that both defines and dissolves the structure’s edge.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570160\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570160\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-21-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Curved modern building with large glass windows and green metal cladding, surrounded by trees, brick paving, and a wooden fence.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-21-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-21-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-21-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-21-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-21-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570159\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570159\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-19-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Compact modern building with a metal exterior and wooden window frame, surrounded by green foliage and trees.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-19-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-19-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-19-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-19-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-19-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=570156\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-570156\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Modern glass-walled garden room with wooden doors, surrounded by trees and situated on a brick path, under a metal roof.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/02/birchpavilion-n4architecture-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, h